    <item>
      <title>印尼维持利率不变，暗示在放松政策前需保持耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/indonesia-keeps-key-rate-steady-to-sustain-rupiah-strength</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼央行维持政策利率不变，并暗示虽然今年晚些时候可能有削减借贷成本的空间，但并不急于放松政策以确保对印尼盾的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/indonesia-keeps-key-rate-steady-to-sustain-rupiah-strength</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 07:30:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福蒂斯丘暂停绿色氢能计划并裁员 700 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fortescue-cuts-700-jobs-and-appoints-new-chief-financial-officer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁安德鲁·福雷斯特 (Andrew Forrest) 正在缩减将澳大利亚矿业公司 Fortescue Ltd. 打造成绿色氢能巨头的计划，他将这一挫折归咎于高昂的能源价格，这导致该集团进行改革并裁员 700 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/fortescue-cuts-700-jobs-and-appoints-new-chief-financial-officer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
